children.name: Fonts (use for Styles; not exported as tokens)

Design tokens are the abstract but shared elements from which your design system is built. Design tokens express any of the individual values that you build from: such as colors, spacing, and typographic features. You should bind tokens to Figma styles whenever and wherever possible to simplify your own design work, but make sure that those are also represented here, as this page is where a developer will pick up tokens with Figmagic.
